dmca.title: Complainant Makes DMCA Claim to Remove Photo of Self
dmca.body:
http://www.jemcopersonnel.com/mugshots/ahmed.jpg
 
My email address: [private]@yahoo.com
 
The image on the above link has my photo. I do not want people to search my name and see my photo. I feel uncomfortable.
 
"I swear, under penalty of perjury, that the information in the notification is accurate and that, for each image identified above, I either own the copyright or am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed." 
 
Thanks,
 
[private]
